{"tid":952324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"應邀來港任演唱會嘉賓　台樂隊不獲發簽證 何韻詩轟港府：音樂交流 驚啲咩呢","createTime":"2018-12-23T04:48:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-23T05:54:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ad68cc6990aa8befa206b26089e3105f002f753e","tid":952324,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T04:48:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181223/20575287\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181223%2F20575287&d=wNStLeKlJHZ9UhUikNHI4ZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=dc096cb8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181223%2F20575287&h=fa57d799\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181223/20575287</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年12月23日 <br />\n應邀來港任演唱會嘉賓　台樂隊不獲發簽證<br />\n何韻詩轟港府：音樂交流 驚啲咩呢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181223/large/23la1p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181223%2Flarge%2F23la1p1.jpg&h=1bd664fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n何韻詩一連六晚在沙田科學園舉行音樂節，惟嘉賓閃靈樂團未能獲發簽證入境。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】在律政司司長鄭若驊僭建事件上主張包容的特首林鄭月娥，在音樂交流上則相當嚴苛。台灣樂隊閃靈樂團五名成員原定來港出席今日的音樂會，惟申請個多月仍不獲香港發出簽證，表演被迫取消。入境處一直無解釋原因，舉辦音樂會的歌手何韻詩怒斥「仆街到冇人有」，並質問政府對一個純音樂交流「驚啲咩呢？」<br />\n記者：盧坤穎　王麗春<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：林昶佐倡台獨當選立委<br />\n<br />\n何韻詩一連六晚在沙田科學園舉行「On The Pulse Of我們正在」音樂節，早前已邀請閃靈樂團出席今晚作嘉賓演出，惟臨時告吹。她在facebook公佈，閃靈的工作證一直不獲批，要取消演出，由周國賢頂上。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181223/large/a0101b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181223%2Flarge%2Fa0101b.gif&h=789234da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181223/large/23la1p2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181223%2Flarge%2F23la1p2.jpg&h=9559631d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台灣閃靈樂團作品以台灣神話、傳說、歷史為靈感主軸，主音林昶佐則主張台獨。CHTHONIC 閃靈fb圖片<br />\n<br />\n團長嘆香港變了<br />\n<br />\n主辦單位上月12日向入境處遞交申請閃靈樂團來港簽證，一直沒正式回覆。何韻詩稱，入境處只曾在本月3日要求她們補上各成員之戶籍謄本，「之後每次追問，職員都只表示『等待上司回覆中』。以我們過往為演唱會其他非港人外籍人士，申請工作證只需一個星期便獲批的經驗和速度來看，這次的處理時間及效率上明顯有別」。<br />\n<br />\n何韻詩說：「其實都預咗Freddy（主音林昶佐）有機會唔批，並且已有plan B，但完全唔覆、拖字訣，真係仆街到冇人有。呢次只係純音樂交流，驚啲咩呢？」她接受本報訪問時形容事件荒謬，「呢個只係一個純藝術嘅音樂節，冇任何政治色彩成份，點解一個純藝術嘅一件事，會因為樂團其中一個人嘅政治立場，而成個團都唔批呢？」<br />\n<br />\n閃靈團長葉湘怡（Doris）接受台灣《蘋果》訪問時說，她們也是第一次碰到這種狀況，以前工作證一、兩個星期就獲批。Doris感慨說，這些年在香港的朋友都說香港變了，「我們也有感覺到，2000年時開始常去香港表演，現在在台灣也看得出來香港政治發展及轉變」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181223/large/a0101a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181223%2Flarge%2Fa0101a.gif&h=f61d3339&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181223/large/1545499367_bcf0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181223%2Flarge%2F1545499367_bcf0.jpg&h=36308100&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n主音：過往很快批出<br />\n<br />\n樂隊主音林昶佐接受《蘋果》訪問時表示，對未能來到香港演出感到可惜。他指出，過往樂團在香港演出了十多場演唱會及表演，入境工作簽證都很快批出。至於是否與閃靈的政治立場有關，他認為問題應該要交由香港政府回答，香港入境處一直沒有向他交代原因，但他指出他們的政治立場在香港過往一直都被廣為報道，不少人都十分清楚，以往工作簽證亦從來沒有問題。<br />\n<br />\n何韻詩好友杜汶澤在facebook留言：「閃靈可以入境才是新聞。」黃秋生則說：「係藝術家都有態度有立場有嘢講㗎啦，冇，不如去補鞋啦。」王宗堯回應稱：「不意外。當政府次次都唔正面回應，次次都話係個別事件，佢哋覺得所有嘢都唔好咁政治化，卻將所有人都政治化。」<br />\n<br />\n入境事務處發言人表示，不評論個別個案。而在審理任何入境申請時，入境處會根據香港法例及現行入境政策，考慮所有與申請相關的因素和情況，以決定是否批准個別人士的申請。<br />\n<br />\n閃靈最後不忘勉勵香港人，在facebook專頁帖文：「最後要感謝所有香港人這幾年來為了民主自由的努力，不止引起全世界的關心，也給予了許多人勇氣。為理想奮鬥的路上，總是會遇到許多的挫敗，但我們會與各位站在一起，香港人加油！而相信有一天，閃靈一定可以再次站上香港為大家演出！」  <br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n林昶佐倡台獨當選立委"},{"pid":"9523a8a7238cc7d33ba57601f895677e2726b20c","tid":952324,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T04:49:53.000Z","msg":"港共垃撚圾"},{"pid":"1153aa73b3ed0eac6907d36e6c488c447d6af4cc","tid":952324,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T04:51:54.000Z","msg":"愛沙尼亞就係唱歌<br />\n唱唱吓由蘇聯獨立<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsimg.ftv.com.tw/manasystem/FileData/News/b77bdef1-a6e3-40f0-bf14-7e23fdb85023.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsimg.ftv.com.tw%2Fmanasystem%2FFileData%2FNews%2Fb77bdef1-a6e3-40f0-bf14-7e23fdb85023.jpg&h=e1210242&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d912005d89541e37c1cf7ccecafc94fd604497a8","tid":952324,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T04:52:44.000Z","msg":"驚呢樣：<br />\n<img src=\"http://timable.com/res/pic/0bb69e30d3a4daee06c0b55e4011707c3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftimable.com%2Fres%2Fpic%2F0bb69e30d3a4daee06c0b55e4011707c3.jpg&h=2d7aa1e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"249ac8aeea2d0ff1c46c3904bae3d292e4ca4742","tid":952324,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T04:53:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />繁體支那政權"},{"pid":"15b75e53c00fb24d5ba668e22f028e7bd8567357","tid":952324,"uid":181318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T04:59:11.000Z","msg":"好撚垃圾"},{"pid":"b0db705cdd2806b5e57af26a20819dd2e0ece0e9","tid":952324,"uid":65530,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T05:10:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"870e8d376d1b35e4bba2ce2d2065640360ee3e99","tid":952324,"uid":35155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0db705cdd2806b5e57af26a20819dd2e0ece0e9","tid":952324,"uid":65530,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T05:10:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T05:16:58.000Z","msg":"標準答案<br />\n真係易做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52cb40211cb2a63cc53b9e1208c3d42fae685b87","tid":952324,"uid":179192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T05:22:53.000Z","msg":"返自己國家都要簽証？"},{"pid":"903de0ac24c080036c0d7fb08ec7ace44c36d99b","tid":952324,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T05:24:36.000Z","msg":"入境處係咪前世未俾人燒過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68eaa1386568a0467b2a1d4f182cc1b40b9f0e5b","tid":952324,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52cb40211cb2a63cc53b9e1208c3d42fae685b87","tid":952324,"uid":179192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T05:22:53.000Z","msg":"返自己國家都要簽証？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T05:39:04.000Z","msg":"證明係不同國家"},{"pid":"bcab0504aad7923db8192f1cc1eec2b00273dfc3","tid":952324,"uid":15691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T05:54:27.000Z","msg":"係咪已經冇方法可以扭轉到呢個局勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}